<p>These are the various categories of sans-serif type. We move forward in time as we go down the list.</p>

<p><img src="http://localhost:4001/svg/kb/classification-sans-variants.svg" alt="Classification Sans variants" width="80%" /></p>

<p>As we move forward in time, the type becomes more fluid and friendly. When type has organic or hand-drawn lines, it’s usually called humanist.</p>

